            <h3>Getting Started</h3>
            <h4>How to Order from Auguri Milk Tea</h4>
            <p>To order, you can visit our shop at the 2nd Floor Calapan Town Center or use our delivery partners. If ordering in-store, simply approach our staff to assist you in choosing your drink. For delivery, select your favorite items on the delivery app and follow the checkout process.</p>

            <h4>Creating an Account (if applicable)</h4>
            <p>If you’re ordering through a delivery platform, you may need to create an account with that service. Simply follow the registration prompts to set up your profile.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="support-container">
            <h3>Navigating the Menu</h3>
            <h4>How to Choose Your Drink</h4>
            <p>Our menu features a wide range of milk teas, fruit teas, and special beverages. You can filter options based on flavor, base (milk or fruit), and toppings. Don’t hesitate to ask our staff for recommendations!</p>

            <h4>Customizing Your Order</h4>
            <p>You can customize your drink by selecting your preferred sweetness level, ice level, and add-ons. Just let our staff know your preferences when ordering.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="support-container">
            <h3>Managing Your Orders</h3>
            <h4>Order Modifications</h4>
            <p>If you need to modify your order (e.g., change toppings or sweetness) before it’s made, please let our staff know immediately. Unfortunately, once an order is completed, we cannot make changes.</p>

            <h4>Canceling an Order</h4>
            <p>For orders placed through delivery platforms, please refer to their cancellation policy. If you’ve placed a direct order, contact us as soon as possible.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="support-container">
            <h3>Common Issues</h3>
            <h4>Order Delays</h4>
            <p>We strive to prepare your orders promptly. However, during peak hours, there may be slight delays. We appreciate your patience!</p>

            <h4>Payment Problems</h4>
            <p>If you encounter issues while making a payment, check that your card or payment method is valid and has sufficient funds. If the problem persists, contact your payment provider or reach out to us for assistance.</p>

            <h4>Allergies and Dietary Restrictions</h4>
            <p>Please inform our staff of any allergies or dietary restrictions when placing your order. We’ll do our best to accommodate your needs.</p>
        </div>
